{"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/threadInit(vtable:)","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"metadata":{"title":"threadInit(vtable:)","platforms":[],"externalID":"s:4GLib10threadInit6vtableySvSg_tF","role":"symbol","symbolKind":"func","modules":[{"name":"GLib"}],"fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"threadInit","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"vtable","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@gpointer","text":"gpointer","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"?)","kind":"text"}],"roleHeading":"Function"},"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"If you use GLib from more than one thread, you must initialize the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"thread system by calling ","type":"text"},{"code":"g_thread_init()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib"]]},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/glib\/threadinit(vtable:)"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"threadInit"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"vtable","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"gpointer","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@gpointer"},{"kind":"text","text":"? = nil)"}]}]},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","text":"Discussion","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Since version 2.24, calling "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_thread_init()"},{"type":"text","text":" multiple times is allowed,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"but nothing happens except for the first call."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Since version 2.32